        "content": "<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"https://wartunelite.wan.com/article/news/aid/8843.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;\">ES</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 16px;\"> / </span><a href=\"https://wartunelite.wan.com/article/news/aid/8844.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;\">PT</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 16px;\"> / </span><a href=\"https://wartunelite.wan.com/article/news/aid/8845.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;\">FR</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 16px;\"> / </span><a href=\"https://wartunelite.wan.com/article/news/aid/8846.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;\">DE</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 16px;\"> / </span><a href=\"https://wartunelite.wan.com/article/news/aid/8847.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 16px;\">TR</span></a></p><h3><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><strong>New Systems and Gameplay &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span></h3><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">I、Marriage System</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">The wait is over! The Marriage System is finally here! Unlocks at Level 25 with NPC “Andrew” as the system’s gateway. Lords who meet certain conditions can propose marriage.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/367914.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/697904.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">After buying a wedding ring, the party leader can speak to Andrew to propose. The Wedding Ceremony can only proceed once the proposal is accepted.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/852118.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/810035.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Married couples can schedule a Wedding Ceremony through Andrew. The Wedding Ceremony lasts 15 minutes and is open to all players.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">II. Marriage Mode</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">When a proposal is successful, the \"Wedding Ceremony Selection\" screen will appear for the couple.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/950280.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Couples can select a time slot for their Wedding Ceremony. Only one wedding event can take place per time slot, so advance reservations are required.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Tips: If you miss your reserved time, it cannot be rebooked.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/851402.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Five minutes before the scheduled Wedding Ceremony, a Wedding Ceremony entry icon will appear in the top-right corner for the couple. Either partner can tap the icon to create the Wedding Ceremony room.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">The room can be created within 5 minutes before or after the scheduled time. If the room isn’t created within this window, the reservation will be forfeited.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Once the room is created, other lords will see an entry point on their main screen to join the Wedding Ceremony.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/818280.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">While in the banquet scene, participants will periodically earn gold.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">A Wedding Heat progress bar will gradually fill during the ceremony and can be boosted by using fireworks items.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Reaching certain milestones on the bar will spawn collectible resources and monsters within the ceremony scene, offering rewards when gathered or defeated.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><strong>III. Happiness</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">After marriage, couples can tap the \"Wedding Ring\" button in the equipment menu to access \"Happiness.\"</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/606604.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Using the \"Rosy Heart\" item increases Happiness XP.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Reaching specific Happiness XP thresholds upgrades the Happiness Level, granting bonus attributes to both partners.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Marriage Daily Activity: \"Heartfelt\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">This daily quiz feature is exclusive to married couples.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">The couple must team up and visit Andrew. Either partner can speak to him to start the \"Heartfelt\" activity.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">You can participate once daily, with 10 questions per session. Matching answers count as correct. Rewards, including \"Rosy Heart\" items, will be sent via mail based on the number of correct answers.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/891125.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><strong> </strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Wedding Ring Skill</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Reaching level 25 and unlocking the Marriage System also grants access to Wedding Ring Skills.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">I、Skill Development</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1、Wedding Ring Skills are developed independently by each partner.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2、Use the \"Heart of Eternity\" item to level up your Wedding Ring. Higher levels unlock new skills or enhance existing ones.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Note: \"Heart of Eternity\" items can be earned through \"Heartfelt\" or purchased in special bundles.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps10.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/856074.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">II、Skill Usage</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1、Only one Wedding Ring Skill can be equipped in battle.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2、These skills can only be activated when both partners are teamed up in the same battle.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps11.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/966729.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">III、Feature Access</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">A new Wedding Ring Skills tab has been added to the skill menu.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/831209.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><strong> </strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><strong> </strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><strong>Feature Expansion</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">I、Gem Levels</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Gems can now be upgraded to levels 9 and 10. Lords can synthesize these high-level gems to enhance their power.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">II、Guardian of Life</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">The Guardian of Life level cap has been increased, allowing lords to become even stronger!</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">III、Dual Mounts</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">When riding a Dual Mount, you can invite a teammate to ride along via the party system. (Currently, a maximum of two people, including the mount owner, can ride.)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><strong>System Optimization</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">I、Marriage System</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1、A dedicated Marriage button has been added to the main interface.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2、A detailed introduction to the Marriage System is now available, helping lords better understand this feature.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps13.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/435820.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">II、Sylph Arena</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Added a skip function, allowing lords to quickly complete challenges.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps14.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/959820.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">III、Domain</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Blitz and Auto Challenge features have been added.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1. Blitz</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(1) For completed levels, lords can use the Blitz feature to instantly collect rewards with one tap.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(2) Blitz consumes one daily entry attempt for the Domain.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(3) Using Domain Keys increases daily entry attempts, thereby increasing Blitz opportunities.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps15.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/26361.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/909759.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2. Auto Challenge</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">For incomplete levels, lords can enable the Auto Challenge option. The system will randomly choose options for you, which may result in either victory or failure.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps17.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/25845.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">IV、Battleground</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1. The daily participation limit has been reduced from 2 battles to 1, with rewards doubled.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2. Additional rewards have been added to battlefield results.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">V、Titles</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1. Title interface layout has been improved, allowing lords to preview title effects.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2. Title attributes now take effect upon activation instead of when equipped, and all activated attributes are cumulative.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/333819.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">VI、Solo Arena</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1、A Refresh button has been added, allowing lords to refresh the current player list.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2、Lords receive 3 free refreshes per day. Once the free attempts are used up, additional refreshes can be purchased up to 3 times per day. Refresh attempts reset daily at midnight.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Note: Each manual refresh resets the cooldown timer.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps19.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/448339.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/606137.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">VII、Guild Battle</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1、Optimized Matchmaking Rules:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2、A personal score system has been added: lords now earn personal score simply by being in the guild war scene.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">3、A new \"no healing\" rule has been introduced: Victorious teams do not recover HP after a battle. Defeated teams will revive with full HP.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">VIII、Blacksmith</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1、The equipment synthesis interface has been improved, with collapsible tabs for equipment sets.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ALLEN~1.CHE\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml63588\\wps21.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><img src=\"https://static-7.wan.com/Ueditorv2/2025/0212/595886.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">(This image is a sample and may differ from the final in-game version.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"><strong>Comprehensive Experience Enhancements</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1. Offline time is now displayed for friends.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2. Optimized dungeon-related interface layouts.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">3. Removed daily purchase limits for Rune Energy.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">4. Improved quest sorting in the quest bar.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">5. Added a Mount Stats Overview button.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">6. Reduced Sylph collection times by 50% in Sylph Atoll.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">7. Optimized the guild interface.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">8. Added new items to the arena shop, including: Rune Shard Pouches, Mount Training Whip Pouches, and Fashion Cores for exchanges.</span></p>",
